==Description== <!--T:17--> 

<!--T:2-->
The [[Image:Part_Mirror.svg|24px]] '''Part Mirror''' command creates a new object (image) which is a reflection of the original object (source). The image object is created behind a mirror plane. The mirror plane may be standard plane ('''XY''', '''YZ''', or '''XZ'''), any plane parallel to a standard plane, or ({{Version|1.0}}) any arbitrary plane by using a reference object.

